Class AquariumManager

java.lang.Object
  Play.AquariumManager

public class AquariumManager
extends Object

Aquarium Manager has been created to take the strain off the simulation class which is our main class. Within this class i add the textures to the aquarium and their behaviours while also creating the aquarium itself

1.5
